Cc mu nn thm khin phi p gc ng
Mi hng l ph kin khng th thiu ca phi p trong th gii hin i. Trong cuc sng
vi v, vic tm kim mt khng gian sng th thi, gip gim cng thng, ci thin sc khe,
l iu m ai cng mong mun. V mt trong nhng cch hiu qu v n gin chnh l s
dng nn thm. y l ph kin trang tr khng gian sng, va c mi thm c trng. V
ngay trong bi vit ny, Mc s bt m nhng mu nn thm khin phi p gc ng.
im tn hai mu nn thm c phi n a chung nht
Angle star: nn thm cho c nng c tnh
Hng u: Cy hoc hng thm nng ngt cng gia v m, ngt ngo ca caramel.
Hng gia: L s ha quyn ca Scla v Vani thm du.
Hng cui: C s kt hp ca g v mt ong to nn v ngt thanh khit, trm m v
ht sc t nhin.
Winter Jasmie Violet: hng phn son n b
Hng u ngt ngo ca hoa nhi n tnh, tinh khit.
Hng gia l hoa cam nh nhng, d chu.
Hng cui l hoa hu thm ngo ngt kt hp vi nhng cnh hoa violet mng manh
v mt cht x hng.
Nhng mi hng ny u l cc loi tinh du thng c s dng nh mt thnh phn trong
kem dng da, m phm. V vy, Winter Jasmine Violet mang li mi hng phn son nh
nhng, vng vn. cng l l do mi hng ny c phi n cc k a chung.
Cc dng nn thm khc c phi n a chung
Mt trong nhng dng nn thm DIY ang c a chung hin nay l dng nn thm nhm
hng hoa. Mi ma hng khc nhau mang n cho chng ta tri nghim khc bit. Cng
Mc im qua nhng mu nn thm p nhm hng hoa hot nht sau y:
1. Lily Of The Valley: Hoa muguet
2. Rose de Mai: Mi hoa hng lng mn
3. Orange Flower & Mimosa: Hoa cam
4. Wild Rose Poppy: Hoa Poppy
5. Lotus Flower: Hng hoa sen thm ngt
6. Ylang Ylang: Hoa hong lan
7. Patchouli Rose: Hoa hng m trn nn g
8. Tuberose White Wood: Hoa hu
9. Dark Amber & Peony: Hoa peony
10. Lavender: Hoa oi hng
Vi nhng mi hng c o v thng ip ngha, nn thm s gip bn truyn ti mi
hng mong mun mt cch tinh t v n tng. Vi bi chia s trn, chng mnh hy vng
gip bn hiu hn v cch lm sao la chn nn thm ph hp nht.
Mc n v cung cp cc loi nn thm thin nhin cao cp cam kt v cht lng vi gi
c hp l nht. Vi chnh sch bo hnh sn phm trn i cng i ng nhn vin am hiu
su v nn, Mc tin rng s lm hi lng nhng v khch hng kh tnh nht.
